We waited for over thirty minutes to get our food, we approached the counter to ask when our food would be ready we were told the order ‚Äúgot lost‚Äù in their system. They put the order in again and waited a few more minutes for it come out. They brought the food out and it was missing sauce packs when we asked for them the employee said ‚Äúit wasn‚Äôt on the order‚Äù we asked if we could we get the sauce we ordered and the employee said no we had to pay for it even though we had already paid for this order when it was initially placed. We said this to the employee who again insisted we had to pay for it. Once we started eating the sandwiches and french fries were cold, the burger patties were also very small. This was a poor experience at best which is unfortunate since we live close by and used to come here frequently.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bruno Sousa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1LD1zrhX0j1I_kM2pP-F0i0tj3CRVrMO7_Y8ewf8RzL3Z1GV_FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's visible that the place is cleaned in the morning but during the day no one it's concerned with that. Oh and they also forgot two things on my order. I don't recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4ru4q1doQQuCIEvHkWNVwGFuMF-Zjo6y3xbDp\u0026fid=0x0:0x956e5ea0a7d0d92f"],"When":"2024-5-25"},{"Name":"Daniel Tarro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYF_2PZVsbXNRrN7DhQ0eXc6U7yB872_x0MGgMPJL3FCRi9EA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Most of my reviews are positive and when I write a bad one it is because it is warranted. It wasn't that busy but it did take about 15 to 20 minutes to get my food at the walk in. When I received my food I got in the car and the fries were warm and the chicken sandwich was cold the tenders were Luke warm and one of them had no chicken just batter. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Bharat Balakrishnan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlqKSx2paT27E6kdcRYZcx9uLNybA-vpB11Z-Io7Y1NvVTOMnW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good Indian food experience. As I am from south India, only I felt the taste being a bit standard but my friends and families enjoyed it. The Indian food is a bit Europeanized so it tastes a bit blunt especially to a person who is from the south of India and lived the whole life cooking with exotic spices.
The customer service was on point. I loved the friendliness and environment of this place.
Although it is a bit pricier, I would visit here again just because of the friendly people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcgXqqDxiJaTLw4HxVhbZIuKcjCKAyhDBY6xUy&fid=0x0:0x277b88b3c78a7e0f"],"When":"2023-12-20"},{"Name":"Robin Rimbaud-Scanner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDuAM1ErwCd5_6O9R8Vcg01h8KpfAPUO_-qvrWTnYBLlu2Ri21=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"As huge fans of indian food we had hoped for something tasty before attending a gig at the music venue just along the road.

Unfortunately the food was rather bland, but then again perhaps we've been spoilt by so many other amazing Indian restaurants from London to New York City.

It was filling, not unpleasant but lacking any real character sadly.

The restaurant itself was busy, but still restful, not stressful music playing either and we weren't hurried out once we finished eating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO22TnnSbeNzPrkzWdrvwqsWgQsMr3wjoB6t0Ad&fid=0x0:0x277b88b3c78a7e0f"],"When":"2023-11-25"},{"Name":"traveling auntie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfYD1AUNMIOoAo4h7jDhqge_TfHVoqLU3MvhP3zhdJxNMC9g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing food & I love that they have lots of great vegetarian/ vegan options. I order from them often for take out, but dined-in when we had visitors.

The atmosphere is also very nice. It‚Äôs a beautiful establishment.

The only I didn‚Äôt love is the customer service. The staff is not very welcoming/friendly at all.

I will return because I like the food and the other Indian restaurant that we used to go to in Heerlen has closed, which is how we found this place. (The owner at the other restaurant was always so kind and friendly to us. I wish we could‚Äôve helped him stay open somehow)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtye8f7J21-xb_Ed68Qh8CMhdhjFt_skRaoomyZroJOCbfbt4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We went there as I watend to experience Indiane cuisine, I specifically expressed that I didn't want lamb, or coriander (as I am Allergic) and I don't like spicy. The waiter said no problem and instead of as ordering he recommended what to order as we had no idea. We had spicy, coriander and lamb!!! We expressed our dissatisfaction!but all they did was just apologise for the waiter being new and that he was learning! I had also ordered the house wine witch was 18‚Ç¨ and was billed 36 ‚Ç¨because the waiter did not understand the difference between house wine and other wines , in the end what they did was a discount of 10% of the whole bill!  I will never recommend this place! I am a professional food taster and wine sommelier, and my conclusion of this restaurant is that you should seek better restaurants, please don't waste your money there. I can recommend much better places at much affordable  prices and probably no one dying of food allergies!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMERBm1Ji7cHEfTejoOY-ZgsLn6bvZgFophPkw&fid=0x0:0x277b88b3c78a7e0f"],"When":"2022-7-19"},{"Name":"Kumar Gaurav Bansal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTuv9ECbWXOD4OF66mrKoI5BCgYH7BC-nQleRf_tnCIGzwGZO5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Poor quality of Naan bread and Palak paneer. The restaurant overcharges so always cross check your invoice (refer attached). After I requested the lady in the restaurant to correct the invoice and get the food packed to takeaway, she got annoyed and refused to do that. Refer hand corrected invoice as attached. STRONGLY NOT RECOMMENDED","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeqQbb0H8FPxCghS31oCZEZI2fZE8dEBvkYEyc&fid=0x0:0x277b88b3c78a7e0f"],"When":"2022-5-15"},{"Name":"Ryan Stephen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvVukT9k2OeVLx5DUC1kVI1NrWpA1P6nRgaF8Zc-4-NXdcvg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"As a huge fan of Indian food, also having had the privilege of visiting India I love the food. I had heard it was a decent Indian restaurant but in honesty it really failed to deliver in terms of quality and flavour. I would not recommend or return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria Blanks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWozlOZqblPyvYquc5N_DXODfisNJXKTMmBMjRN5_CgjtHXjrBd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"So disappointed‚Ä¶

I read the reviews and was so excited to try this place. It took 20 minutes for them to even ask what we wanted to drink. After an 1 and 23 minutes I finally asked how much longer they thought it would take. They then went to the counter and brought my food out, cold. If that wasn‚Äôt bad enough the portions were small. If I‚Äôm paying 20euro I expected to be full  or be able to take food home. Lastly it was bland‚Ä¶. all around disappointing. Garlic Naan was the only thing worth a thing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nisha Ram","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJ3MyxGmkvAPPGW8oPaOc_9-UvDhURvySz1xh8XFS5cSXewN_i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food is not Indian at all. Long wait time of one and half hours .","Images":null,"When":""}]

As a very picky person i loved how welcoming the staff and place was, the food was so delicious and definitly made with love! Will for sure dine here again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jodi Hendriksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHJE9KTiaPGcGfGyYFWGEjspQdeaTrO89wOZQWh2WUC2RINQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Geweldig knus restaurantje gelegen in hartje Heerlen! Deze dames maken overheerlijke gerechten, je kunt niet alleen terecht voor burgers.. ze hebben een gevarieerd menu met o.a. super lekkere belegde broodjes en zelfgemaakte soep. Ze hebben ook een uitgebreid aanbod met vegan gerechten! Ontbijt, lunch diner, je kunt voor alles terecht. Je voelt meteen een warm welkom, ze maken een praatje met de klanten en zorgen dat je een hele fijne ervaring hebt terwijl je de smaaksensatie ervaart van hun top gerechten. Ze doen dit met ontzettend veel passie en liefde, en dat proef je!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLcEH1j-L-vZFp79Q8fHFD7BzN9UWnuNdFpYlK&fid=0x0:0x3739c2e23f9e1f61"],"When":"2025-1-12"},{"Name":"Angie Vos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIychj4p__7AoEbz0ltYD2Hh1M2hpJEOUjDhHH4eAkM-jkzrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vandaag voor de eerste keer geweest. Ik ben echt ontzettend positief verrast.

We hadden het broodje cheese steak. En OMG! Ik had me hier al op verheugd en hoge verwachtingen. Maar hij was me toch lekker. Een groot broodje, niet te hard gebakken. Overladen met gebakken groenten, steak en een overheerlijke kaassaus die smeu√Øg bleef. Er zat wat aardappelsalade bij. Ook de burgers, koffie en smoothies die voorbij kwamen, zagen er goed uit. Drinken serveren ze met het blikje en mooie glazen. Prijs - kwaliteit echt prima. En ik hoorde de opmerking dat wat men niet op kreeg, dat ook mee naar huis genomen kon worden.

De sfeer is heel erg fijn. Lichte zachte inrichting, zachte stoffen stoelen. En de chef en bediening staan er met plezier. En dat je oprecht welkom bent, dat voelde ik.

De service was ook top. Door ziekte heb ik graag wat afstand van mensen en moet ik mijn eigen mes mee nemen omdat horecamessen vaak bot zijn. Hier werd niet moeilijk over gedaan, ik werd op mijn gemak gesteld en er werd rekening mee gehouden. Overigens zijn hun rvs messen hier heel scherp ‚úÖÔ∏è. Ik ben niet op het toilet geweest dus daar kan ik helaas niets over zeggen.

Ik ga hier zeker nog vaker eten en kan het iedereen aanraden.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5Ro8uOh8LfRZuMBFK33l3gXh_k6nZc_Eo2wOg&fid=0x0:0x3739c2e23f9e1f61"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Chanti Polonius","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGaaIW6zce4-yn46fooH2lybRB9HRWUFI-zf4vHwYsFi5giA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vandaag een bezoek gebracht bij Dimis overloaded. Bij de vraag wat ze mij zouden aanraden kreeg ik de mogelijkheid om te proeven of ik het auberhaupt lekker vind voordat ik kon bestellen. Prijskaart is het bedrag meer dan waard voor wat je krijgt. Ik heb de burger beef and mushrooms gegeten. Burger was lekker sappig, mushrooms met de kaassaus en uien gebakken in allioli maakte de broodje compleet. Echt een aanrader. Voor lekker, vers en ruim belegd broodjes kun je ook bij hun terecht.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWiVG-epPRr0KSnIpgHPPlN6NXtGNwsScpOy6w&fid=0x0:0x3739c2e23f9e1f61"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Jua De La Fuente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAlru2Hw7u598M7Xyx9CdpK4dXEOwHwEleQf5YhDpPCMNd0sfolg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vandaag snel ons eten gekregen en dat tijdens de opening ! [{"Name":"Sindy Hermans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrhZAaFoTXeDd4hte9q1aB7rAQH_c31kdETCQ5vaT3G3vJfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Nog maar eens geprobeerd en gisteren een lunch genuttigd. Ik nam de wrap krokante kip. De wrap zelf was van bieten gemaakt en zag er mede daardoor mooi uit. De smaak viel helaas enorm tegen. De kipkrokant moest ik zoeken tussen de enorme hoeveelheid aan sla. Er waren welgeteld drie stukjes kipkrokant in de wrap verwerkt. De hoeveelheid aan groenvoer was onsmakelijk. Het geheel werd hierdoor zompig, daar de sla veel vocht bevatte en koelkast koud was, nauwelijks smaak had (geen dressing of anderzins) en de kipkrokant juist warm was. Kortom, het heeft niet gesmaakt. De bediening was vriendelijk, dat dan weer wel. Toen ik bij de bediening aangaf dat de hoeveelheid aan sla echt overdone was, knikte ze instemmend en liet weten het aan de keuken door te geven. Op de foto de sla die uit de wrap kwam die over was, ik had al veel van deze sla wel opgegeten. Mijn partner had de club sandwich, deze was redelijk te noemen. Hij vond het brood droog en de saus te min. Jammer, we kwamen hier vroeger heel graag. Voor de prijs valt de kwaliteit helaas tegen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPklnUYvDEng5_SOxeJphpYWTY6Aq4A-lPMxrOC&fid=0x0:0x142809910b12228b"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Sander Pleijsier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKtTNkzdkduVxU1vORa9ZBFFQbQl1oQdLS135qP5yAKqZmdU_ziA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Steak tartare zoals 'ie moet. Joop Wiersma","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wiel van Booden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIIUMLtpFHS73vl-g-lneuXouy7y6CdJ0u0SM3ctQm4YQUtyne=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We zijn hier gaan lunchen op zondag middag. De dikke frieten waren vandaag helaas uitverkocht. Het smaakte prima. Ook op de tonijn salade die mijn vrouw had besteld was niks aan te merken, of het moet zijn dat het best veel was üòâ.

Highly recommended!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNigW6I9AiADHb14uzkilNBSJDwSNtbTikr16Gn\u0026fid=0x0:0x5b70f3853f309ece"],"When":"2023-12-26"},{"Name":"Jay-J Garrett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIg9hEFbl8NRSf9b7HB3jRvADC_4tbxEV9piquPKKUkH5sV5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time ordering tonight. Really good! Freshly made and very tasty. Friendly delivery service, would definitely recommend and will order again probably very soo! 5/5","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmtOu-VSxcqdVKH01os58zgrB8sdf21s6am8ZiXfWL5jyTug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Het restaurant heeft een mooie inrichting en ligt net buiten de stad, waar in de omliggende straten voldoende gratis parkeerplaatsen beschikbaar zijn. In de straat zelf geldt betaald parkeren. Het eten is smaakvol en de prijzen zijn redelijk, maar de bediening laat te wensen over. Ondanks dat er maar twee tafels bezet waren en  twee mensen in de bediening werkten, duurde het lang voordat we een tweede drankje konden bestellen. Dit werd zelfs opgemerkt door andere gasten die zelf naar voren liepen om een bestelling te plaatsen. Dit is jammer, want het eten is lekker.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFHZFMAOqgiSpuudX0cDG0HlkFUiZvSWcE3QNI\u0026fid=0x0:0x5b70f3853f309ece"],"When":"2025-1-21"},{"Name":"John Goessens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVHff6MwY4dfGJryIwzwo6hGGGnED3ZYpL8qK3ZbUNxwlzmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eerste keer eten gehaald. Was erg lekker. Alhoewel ik niet ter plaatse gegeten heb, was de sfeer binnen gezellig en mooi verzorgd. We gaan er vast vaker naar toe. Een aanwinst voor Heerlen!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Manocher Jabbarzadeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8q-SnDfiJmT1PeVBUnwTxdug0CuPSvKKHTku_JJD-X3ZTrDMTjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"De gehavende kebab met rijst, salade en vers tandooribrood(Naan), net als Iraanse kebab en eten, alles was echt geweldig. [{"Name":"Siobhan Whelan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVRO7s5X6Amr71tQ9kslPDEJUaPhzdn4OSEb0g4mE1orhHeQ9O=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped in here for an impromptu meal as I had never eaten out in Heerlen before and was not disappointed. The decor is lovely, giving a nice relaxing and friendly atmosphere. The staff (including chef) were very friendly, welcoming and attentive, speaking Dutch and really good English (thank you!).
The food was excellent, coming out in a timely manner, it looked amazing and there was no compromise on the flavour.  Was very happy with the portions and price point for the exceptional tasting food. [{"Name":"shaun allen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuu1ypIBtntNDJqSAx6-GrCkemQIXGbzjBcPJYflNfMBzeHpPE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food never arrived kept being told it‚Äôs on its way absolutely rude when questioned do not use no customer care at all","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Derwort","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlXVQEaA-OTQYtANx3YQG8yqC6Nh2HSKC8YwGAKv9KKO2ME30B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, friendly staff and not expensive!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"vincent smeets","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsucQqMCUFJls__jiTJQkxhg48u9NXMR8Vir2uy4rIKY7hAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Vanavond besteld bij Bolzano, eigenlijk vanmiddag maar het wachten duurde 2 uur dus inmiddels is het al avond. De ervaring was zo SLECHT dat ik google heb gemailed om een mogelijkheid te maken om 0 sterren te geven. En dat is nog zacht uitgedrukt. Ik heb een keer gebeld om te vragen hoe het met mijn bestelling was, toen werd ik erg onvriendelijk te woord gestaan door een vrouw die zei dat het er dadelijk aankomt. Echter duurde het nog 1 uur na het gesprek. Toen de pizza en kapsalon werden bezorgd kwamen wij tot de ontdekking dat alle reviews klopte namelijk: een koude pizza met een te zachte maar toch aangebrande korst. Hierbij kregen we ook nog een cadeautje namelijk een mooie haar van iemand uit de keuken. ( zie afbeelding 2 in het midden). De kapsalon was wel lekker. Maar nadat mijn vriendin een haar vond in haar pizza, heb ik toch iets minder ervan genoten. Ik zou dit restaurant echt ten zeerste afraden. [{"Name":"Laura Belli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNFykEfXGAZiuLsuzlyvkJLQJl_W9C-fEPzQiKOchEAEm44uuv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A small but cozy restaurant, with authentic Italian food. The atmosphere is very characteristic and the staff was very gentle. The food was served to us quickly. Grazie ancora per la cena!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Willy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjtaw0HLw2e-PMj6tEvSpRnrMtqItcedpR47fUkDyQiZ39rPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"After a long working day, I invited my brother for a dinner and I told him there is a close pizzeria restaurant seems nice but I never tried it before, he said okay lets try it.

First we waited for more than 10 minutes before the waitress ask us what to drink, and after we ordered the drinks we waited around another 10 minutes to get the drinks, we ordered two pizzas and  fish soup as a starter, after another 15 minutes we received a few pieces of leftovers bread and some garlic butter, the bread was very dry and not clean, there was some blue dots on it and some bird feather stuck in it, as you see it in the picture.

after around 15 minutes the woman came to us and said we are very sorry the waitress forgot to give your order to the kitchen and it's going to take a bit longer.

we waited for around half an hour to receive the soup, it taste canned and very fishy, we asked when the pizza are going to be ready, they said soon!

after around 15 other minutes, we received the pizza which it was also doesn't worth all that waiting, it was very normal pizza that you can find in any cheap restaurant.

Finally I will not recommend this restaurant to anyone, specially if you are inviting someone and you don't want to be ashamed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"vincenzo rotondo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiFgERWhf6VvPSGsen9JyjFugZJBL-sCMCKWdJVZSIDvjFXx2x=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm italian, i traveled around the world. Here in HEERLEN I found the really trhue italian food. Seems to stay in Campania, region of south Italy. For One moment I though to be in Italy and not in the Beautifull North Europe. Congratulation to Nando and to  all the staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theo Goossen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiYjHQRq-BVNFzUeKBmI2SCa_7QimL3vUNN-2no1V5xKbaDf3y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Da Nando has been a known value for ages. They let us bring in a pizza since we were there right when they opened and they don‚Äôt serve food. I will return if I am back in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrt-e56NIx82gw2sQ-D__cWItiA0MeTkdsiYgG&fid=0x0:0xb82251cdc00b785d"],"When":"2019-2-25"},{"Name":"Terri Tells","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKIdusp1A28U6ktsAtUYCeSVRh38DaqR5GCS5SUK3Wt9-ooSLM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Heerlen is the kind of city that when you look for a place to socialise, you'll probably end up saying:  "Let's just go to Erin's Isle."

Don't get me wrong, there are plenty of fun places in Heerlen to go, but each place is right for a certain type of people. Erin's Isle is a niche caf√© great for people who feel the rest isn't right for them.

There's rock, there's metal, there's all kinds of beer (and some good wine for fancy drinkers like me). Walls plastered with rock caf√© decor and the chance to request your favourite songs. There's a lounge square in the middle with deep couches, and you'll often find people gathering to play cards.

The staff is approachable and casual. If you go there often enough, they'll become your friends. Though a little casual: when asked for beer snacks in the form of crisps, we literally got two layes baggies. Good thing we knew how to make a makeshift bowl!

Beer bingo is comical, and all it takes is ordering a few special beers to participate.

If you have no idea where to go, come see if you're right for this place. [{"Name":"Red Queen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeroVWTTGHj9jrSB0NSZY9B0riSie7J25PCrDPcymInX-nfJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"From the time of order, to receiving the order, to dine in, it took 30 mins. Slowest fast food I ever got. The quality of the food was terrible, I left half of it. Portion sizes of the coffee was a joke. Then for deposit (statiegeld) you don't get the money back at KFC, no you need an app tikki for this, unbelievable. This whole experience needs three words, terrible never again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNp-hGTnGPku-Ju9wLuTKhNwli5WVvrWAwiyV64&fid=0x0:0x90f2556e0197d692"],"When":"2024-3-1"},{"Name":"Neeraj Bangera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyoE-pFXc1IfhEMMTthg5a4onhz61OJ7CwYzOjj3MQr6xxFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"My friend and I ordered the original bucket of 10 pieces, the chicken was too salty we didn't realise it initially as we were hungry but after the 6th piece we were dependent on the Apple spritz to complete the entire bucket. The chicken is not so crispy either :(","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Macaroni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKG-hvKUY45QYu8gsoydW15LjbQlb7fL190BQ8ghr2g_gxHrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Friendlier than the other locations!
Also a little tip.. Order happy meals to save money! You get a decent amount of food for the price. A half corn cob alone is like 3.50 but you can have it in a happy meal for no extra cost. Check app for coupons also

Editing to add.. Today I received a drink full of ants... I had to tell the lady they were there. In a see thru cup.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ricardo Graus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXemvKsb_B5I1N6Of54cZq14sPb9ZmdmtIAKDbzrfSkpmdtb_CN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"After my first review, a lot has changed. Since a couple of weeks the people at the drive through only seem to talk English. Not a problem for me, but I can imagine people running into issues with ordering because of this. Also, when the restaurant opened, the employees were friendly and answered questions without any issues. Nowadays you can barely get any contact with employees, because they are too busy talking to each other. The place also does not look clean anymore.

My girlfriend has gotten sick from eating products from them two weeks in a row. I have no idea whether they changed something regarding recipes or not, but it's strange she never had this at other KFC's, nor at this place before the "changes".","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suresh MIx","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7YI4OQAiFJ1X-hlrLs9Kvb9HO3S071YLFiyTtv5wRSt4yBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"KFC is running a scandal with the cups given for drinks.. They take 1 Euro during the order, but refuse to pay it back immediately on return of the cups.. giving a machine which doesn't work for some cups (before they don't work for some qr codes on cups) and then you have to give your bank account to some stupid app (all the trouble to get back 1 Euro). Scandal.. [{"Name":"Laura Macaroni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKG-hvKUY45QYu8gsoydW15LjbQlb7fL190BQ8ghr2g_gxHrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Giving 3 stars to not punish the GOOD employees but I just had an appalling experience with a female worker. So rude, giving attitude to me because she has to refill the lettuce. Screaming at me for daring to ask for ingredients on my sub. I asked for another employee and he came and handled it at the end. He's a gem, the other guy also. I come in often and have always breen treated with professionalism and kindness. Now I'm afraid to return because of this girl. I'm so sorry you had to do your job!  I work in the food service industry myself and I would absolutely be fired for displaying such behavior to a customer.

Photos included of how much lettuce  I received after asking for extra. This was my daughter's sub. Worker  didn't flip out on me until I dared to ask for lettuce on mine as well though she gave attitude from the very first moment.. Then my cheesy rollup was with not enough cheese and not even melted. I said nothing because I was scared of her. I've never been treated so badly in my life. I go here at least once a week and spend over 20 euro each visit. I choose this location because the staff are the friendliest. Until today. Please cut that weed from your garden.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOasHDdEwO1sqtCxTgXiU3Z8kVBeJvMAQ4xjuB&fid=0x0:0x2bc0f11b7cc19b31"],"When":"2025-1-10"},{"Name":"david schulz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeqATtipvD6BAbAJlK3yZ5Zsos90Ny5FpsC3EsANtMug-izg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"as a Subway, the ingredients were fresh and great. Service was poor, no greetings or goodbye not even a simple ‚Äúenjoy your meal‚Äù
Service was also very slow.. two employees in the store with one sat on her phone.

Resturant itself looks very dated, untidy with food packaging and empty drink bottles left on the tables from previous guest and a big puddle of water from the rain.

I took my order to go, having to ask for a napkin and bag. Sub was wrapped loosely and the box of sides wasn‚Äôt constructed correctly so everything got soggy.

Got my regular order but it didn‚Äôt taste as good as when I order from my regular subway. There were also olives and other veg I didn‚Äôt order inside the sandwich which threw me off a little. I hate olives ha.

Overall not q great experience, maybe some better staff training and cleaning/maintenance will help. I visited between 2/3pm on a rainy Monday afternoon so I can‚Äôt imagine visiting during dinner/lunch periods or the weekend. I tried it once but unfortunately won‚Äôt be returning and will stick to my regular location even if I have to cycle a little further.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Murdock Hornocks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZjiT8bOJVHoQXN0pb0bs_FUdF7Z8FpnIPYc9mdgXC-lQUMSi2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food as usual.

[{"Name":"Aaron Larkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX70nhFut_F64tHtXO0yW0olW8gslt5LZb8AoyD6c4KyW8rSorq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love this place! The food is to die for. The atmosphere once the kitchen closes is the best I've found in Heerlen with live music and good drinks menu what more can you ask for! On a busy night the service can be abit slow but the staff work tirelessly and always have a smile.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcxeZus49LcX54QNcSr3fs22sLOJFzXdOJmlFp&fid=0x0:0xc5e59fdfb3044e90"],"When":"2021-11-28"},{"Name":"Arjan van de Rest","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKpqcPLhAkYOg3HgnI4vRlP34BrYYyymY_h629B6O7LzF3twQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great location for a night out with your partner or a group of friends

The ambiance is excellent and the staff overly friendly.  The food is delicious

And then there is the live music. They have an app to request songs, and they are very ambitious to play those.

We came on a social deal, and will come back again for more.

Definitely worth 5 stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MarSzumilas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwkxqgbIWp1GzQOHXcp2gccN9HXXK1Gtixa9pIbUAf6CE2fA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food was ok, but waiting time and service was a disaster. We didnt like it at all. Live music was good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Madina Malacarne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuWq1xn2La6tJKFcbkaagZWfliylbJv18RcjnmmYXS3Xl2lJkC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really fun time everytime we go","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave Malek-VitaCucina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIQuicXL28IFNwKgmEMxtbqof2vs4E8m7BDZGSDHT-IT9H4eCW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Live Piano's Heerlen,

Leuk concept: Lekker tafelen met live muziek.
Via een QR-code kun je verzoekjes indienen deze komen dan vanzelf bij de pianist terecht.

Het eten: Het eten ziet er goed verzorgt uit en smaakt ook zeker prima, er is genoeg keuze voor iedereen is er wel iets. Jammer genoeg was mijn biefstuk alleen niet gebakken zoals gevraagd deze was helaas wel heel erg rauw in plaats van medium.

Het personeel: Het personeel doet hun werk prima, zelfs toen ik aangaf dat mijn biefstuk erg rauw was schrok men hier niet van. Er werd meteen aangeboden om een nieuwe te bakken (prima) toen ik aangaf dat dit niet hoefde (mijn eigen keuze) werd er gevraagd of ze er iets anders tegenover konden zetten. Het volgende drankje werd dan ook niet op de rekening gezet. Opgelost zoals het hoort dus.

Minpuntjes: Helaas vond ik de toiletruimte erg vuil ogen, en dit terwijl wij de eerste klanten van de avond waren. Vooral de spiegel was erg vettig.

Door de muziek is het een erg leuke ervaring (gezellige zaak).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfSV7kSvZJIY9fKaIZk1_lCoLEB2iCGjyvvFkT&fid=0x0:0xc5e59fdfb3044e90"],"When":"2022-8-7"},{"Name":"Bjorn Geraerts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLA1MI5pekRUncZBI0nJpWuIGOHQPlijASMAPvyFQXC6dq7vw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ik ben hier op vrijdag 10 maart geweest met mijn vriendin als verassing en het was echt een hele fijne avond - op het begin is het er rustig en kan je fijn dineren en tegen de avond is het ook zeer gezellig maar wat drukker kan je ook dansen als je dat wil - als je kan zingen geven ze je daar ook de kans voor. Het eten was ook lekker alleen niet zo veel keuze. Er zijn ook slechte reviews maar trek dat je niet aan om tot hier te komen. Wij komen nu vaker ! Om eens bij te babbelen kun je inderdaad beter ergens gaan waar er geen live muziek is","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2TFgjM3FSyPNRN2kbQQxU-hkGytu_7Mv9RlQM&fid=0x0:0xc5e59fdfb3044e90"],"When":"2023-3-15"},{"Name":"Robert Schwab","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINyXOXLX-SQ5mWW8AXr6RCZxxsdCmKKu85fgv58p4EdX_OoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Aanrader om een keer uit eten te gaan wanneer je zin hebt in een avondvullend programma. Leuke live muziek, veel afwisseling in artiesten en verzoeknummers. Eten en service waren goed, maar de sfeer overtreft beiden.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMugE8_II-rrF8k3ChUEKoiMxJaVh-FgFKqLMfB&fid=0x0:0xc5e59fdfb3044e90"],"When":"2023-6-10"},{"Name":"Pauline Louis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnzWQAwdM97RosswUUxYXSSurNGbRLyE2JHOtKjkQ0VlH24xfd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Geweldig, ik denk dat Heerlen niet weet wat ze voor een pareltje ze hebben in hartje centrum. Waar kun je lekker eten met live muziek elk weekend? Vandaag SD Deal gehad maar je kon gewoon kiezen van de kaart. Eten was super lekker, leuke bediening. 2 mannen en een vrouw die voor muzikale avond zorgden. Leuke interactie onderling maar buiten dat hadden ze een mooie stem.
Ik heb er nog 2 gekocht en ga heel graag weer terug","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCBQBp60UqFBrXT8PhRtY8R9eTmBvWUS5jDY3Z&fid=0x0:0xc5e59fdfb3044e90"],"When":"2023-7-1"}]

In Heerlen al veel zaken bezocht,maar wat betreft originele gerechten en het brengen ervan,1 van de beste! Het personeel is vriendelijk en behulpzaam. De prijzen liggen misschien iets hoger als elders,maar je krijgt er ook een mooi plaatje voor in de plaats,zeker en vast een aanrader üëç","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPckLq_6srBcriarQgFLI-LcuoetqwUZOH9UkVE&fid=0x0:0x8a81ccbbbd60a86c"],"When":"2024-12-29"},{"Name":"Elise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLKRA5UCnoNt15ViaGB1PVPXZIkOGhvcdPTgjQ36-67oSTPzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hebben hier gisteren gegeten en het was heerlijk! Gastvrouwen/gastheren waren vriendelijk.

Puntje van aandacht: Ons is uitgelegd dat je het eten in delen kan bestellen, maar toen we aangaven oester/brood eerst te willen laten komen, kwamen de andere gerechten erg rap erna. Dit voelde zeer gehaast en vonden we jammer. Voor de volgende keer zullen we bestellen wat we eerst op tafel willen hebben en daarna de rest. Verder was het eten dus echt top, chapeau voor de keuken!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzDUsR41eyk4ssXQtFDyckp58VonpzsafgP0wT&fid=0x0:0x8a81ccbbbd60a86c"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Mark F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAoFKf39Q4phEblMc23Sh48DR8i6fUl_40oDjQwoJVU9CZYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wij zijn hier met een grote groep geweest van 16 personen. Op het terras was het prima vertoeven.

Ook het assortiment aan speciaal biertjes is goed. As always, the first-class service, exquisite snacks, delicious food and warm environment.  The restaurant is on the fifth floor with a sweeping view of the city.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMi5W-9VQRPbX9PpKb-1MOO-8NRKT2ze1nldxCO&fid=0x0:0xcf68cefb29a2796b"],"When":"2024-1-28"},{"Name":"Diana Pereira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUhwHRl13mFlZZahUOm62iRIWnL9txwiTKu5kEK5oE82JudA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommended!
This place is just perfect : great location with an amazing view over Heerlen,  impeccable and friendly service and amazing food. Flavors are just right and creative. I love how they keep the menu seasonal whilst keeping an eye on public favorites.
There's definitely a mediterran touch to it (from ingredients to cooking techniques).
Fries are mandatory...and not just because you're in the Netherlands :)
The white chocolate and passion fruit martini is the best cocktail i've ever had. Love it as a dessert.

I've visited in numerous occasions and i have never been let down.
One of the best options in the area, if not the best.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTuu8dbr02nGGgCxIHtshSjbjnB4xfj_mkFBPh&fid=0x0:0xcf68cefb29a2796b"],"When":"2023-3-4"},{"Name":"Roselyne Rheaume","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWknrtOhaNsJW7ag-l_Bg8HYURKyx1elKq164ZmhHCyrqYr1Fm-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food, beautiful presentation, great flavors. Fine food in a relaxed  atmosphere. Had the 5 course menu, and loved it all!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCWFKj0hQY1LMyoV1LcdrCOtW_IJ2F8VQiLTc_&fid=0x0:0xcf68cefb29a2796b"],"When":"2023-7-5"},{"Name":"Yannik Schmidt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEYGX-kGD4-94QDxMTyhvepymq-Yrbfi3IJ3AFTROy41_0IA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, food and staff. Would definitely recommend this to everyone that is looking for a finer dining experience in Heerlen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgPKPHr2TnOXNlEh_5CNvOjHxDPzvBsj0-IZL1&fid=0x0:0xcf68cefb29a2796b"],"When":"2023-5-10"}]

Interesting modern design. Good location in the center of Heerlen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1VXqI2VP9_7XPfL8lSwf2IcXazk4028BwASdl&fid=0x0:0x23fbbef9b55f988a"],"When":"2023-4-1"},{"Name":"Jonas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrCA_p3U3FiOK1-u_ZxoxVESjMSCHF1O9jYCqaInLDZYqFow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Extremely friendly staff and very nice atmosphere. Food however was mixed. Therefore i am writing the review hopefully to make owners and kitchen aware do they can adapt if wanted. As ut would be a shame if this place is let down by its food. We had several starters and the feedback here is 50/50. Two of them were amazing the other ones were ok but kind of blend. One example was the crab with salad. Sounded very nice on the menu but crab was blend and salad no dressing or very little. On the other hand calamari were amazing and the other dips for the bread too. Scampi on the other hand blend again. Presentation etc. very nice so nothing to change there.
For the main the muscles were amazing. Really big im size (the actual muscles, so not taking about the portion size here but portion was generous in case you would like to know. On the other hand our two friends who had different cuts of meats I think one of them was the Brazil one mention again that flavor was blend and sides all tasted the same as the meat. We actually tried it and can confirm this. And again salade not dressed. If you put salad on thrn plate then it needs dressing otherwise it is just leaves... steak Tatar was unfortunately a let down as well. Very blend and the few drops of dressing not enough. Egg was missing.
Overall still a nice experience as the staff was very very friendly and professional. And again some of the food was very tasty. Moscow Mules were very good too. I wrote the long review because I like the place and the good vibe there so hoping that owner and kitchen do something a out this. Taste your own food and adapt accordingly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aradossa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsXeZylJ0rTtUHmPnyzspkAreVYTobgRRyFrUQU_7Z_Dt32HoA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best spareribs I‚Äôve ever eat. Waiter was attentive and informative! The food was excellent and we enjoyed my visit! I highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"N R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpHIgEDZT-RO70VwVejWpKlB5kIwBj7ZvC6rZ0VwnptLICpcYI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The beef steak was delicious and tasty. Good job! The delivery guy was very kind too, even when he forgot to bring the Coca Cola we ordered, he was back in less than 5 minutes and brought an additional Coca Cola.

I definitely recommend this restaurant and will order again. Thank you!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olizy Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsnf5DPzgL1A0NbDlAx38y5Gd51Lw-SUMDOHJYpn9_bZiUoalang=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went there for dinner when we tried to find a place to eat. Was a great experience. Starting with the friendly staff and ending with a quick and amazing service.
Of course you pay for what you eat.
And i am so proud to say that was one of my best experiences.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wenny Sumarni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhhfzUXFbu-u9d7j-Pb5_DdOreY-MNVGpw6dAFfhRuufY07lV43w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Bad service from the owner,  we certainly will not come back.

We came in from the cold and I ordered Turkish tea on the menu,  and he said they don't have Turkish tea but they have wine.  I don't drink alcohol,  so I just ordered coffee. We'd noticed they kept pushing on the wine sales throughout the meal.  Appetizers and main courses went fine but we had to remind the waiter & waitress of our desserts 3 separate times and it finally came more than 1 hour after our main courses.  The owner brought them and he was not even apologetic,  he just said 'you have to wait for good food.'  I wondered if the couple next to us were served bad food because they had 4 courses,  came later than us, but were already done and had left when we were still waiting for our 3rd course dessert.  And it was an under cooked apple struddle,  not particularly warm when served,  definitely not worth the wait.

The young waiter &  waitress were friendly and nice but an arrogant owner does not make this a welcoming place.
Avoid if you can.
Highly not recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Kimmel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGymZA6-3104U6TNSvX3ympjHZDrM7YuLCnZsgYjRDvcQn4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice little restaurant, good food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7BFq9ysX_2v3DDXbRsZzi_h680YYAlsX23lyH&fid=0x0:0x9394d7d09a5e1b23"],"When":"2019-5-27"},{"Name":"Chris Brunne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEJowiZ1FXVM2kVXX4i-_vQE0O2pUtF-KUNdtUi_A6SO33XQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It was ok. When we didn't order wine with the main dish the waiter was a little condensending.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Moriel La Rosa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzVpyqQlbKx9VnLCalJWlN7vwgNIKwwf5n6aWvbfUujuqKRPq4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can't be happier:) Gluten free options are possible, quick service, very nice menu and more authentic Italian food than in any other places. Very nicely decorated.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharath Rokkam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJksixzp2Z2H7UE1Ue175IgysRoKWGtEoK3iRQCzYKHZvoUHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of the best Italian restaurants in this region.
The place has a very good Ambience.
Hospitality is great with some wonderful staff.
Location is very close the city center of Heerlen. A challenge is the parking spots near the restaurant in weekends if you want to park on the street, you have a parking complex nearby.
We have been here several times and every time the food is amazing as always.
Being a vegetarian, I find lot of options in Pizza and Pasta.
You have try the wood fire Pizza here.
Do not forget to end the dinner with an Amazing and Authentic Tiramisu as a desert, you will remember it for your life.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRKAjPpST6F-ilg5id_QROH1Ygjvr5VJtWd_jg&fid=0x0:0x3f1251b0c1eee4b1"],"When":"2022-10-3"},{"Name":"Tom Derwort","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlXVQEaA-OTQYtANx3YQG8yqC6Nh2HSKC8YwGAKv9KKO2ME30B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, great atmosphere and great staff! In the city centre, near the high street and just around the corner of bars/nightclubs and parking garages. What more could you ask for?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNU2QkkbkrE_tjglptJkcvvqy8wfe3bjBWKkItO&fid=0x0:0x3f1251b0c1eee4b1"],"When":"2022-6-1"},{"Name":"Nadia Tafesse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtmD2TkHBcQbesg_UasxEk-yBsAmRRpXQbH_qQQWNUzXWcFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Went for a family birthday dinner a couple of weeks ago. Service by the waiter (jasper I think?) was SCANDALOUS! DISRESPECTFUL! Honestly I was so speechless that I had to ask if he even was Italian (which he obviously wasn‚Äôt but of course for entertainment kept saying ‚ÄúSI SI SI‚Äù).
And if you‚Äôre POC, please don‚Äôt go! I could tell there was a difference in treatment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Graham L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNCEIP6-LzGmoVnusHCg6AutKri2AA-T4hn4kTsA36F-FNekT2IQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was good, but pasta portions were small, especially for the price
Staff were lovely and cheerful.
Bruschetta was a bit tasteless, though a good size. No home-made bread.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Hidalgo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0EDF7uZZyaJslqP2PbBwunIWeyjDcDrQRXQZol-X4Nzj6BhQnPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went with my work colleagues and they were very attentive and kept the dishes coming all at once for each course.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raj SAYS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInzm97pFm7HrN-wLM168_iarcYNcdwxgUSMRWiaHyB7DAK2PmN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We orders Pizza n drinks, Felt v.good.

Awesome service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOalE5P5g8j2oWVBqFeuyeNwwpTFSTLxOyk0JuY&fid=0x0:0x3f1251b0c1eee4b1"],"When":"2019-1-25"},{"Name":"Pieniek Pieniek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJsssoSaC9UXg-MescYpUAkFw5WYdRl9DrESb3hcrrKQXiXDW4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beste pizza van Heerlen!
Great pizza, still haven't tried different dishes, but pizza is excellent. Pricewise also reasonable. Usually pretty busy, lots of people, if you want a table on the weekend best make a reservation a day before. I guess the fact that it usually is pretty full is a proof the place is worth visitingüòâ
Very
friendly staff, highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Remy Geraeds","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxtu846AWK8k6EKFUjIYsiIhSaVa9M5cLFoWrUkVKSb1uH0Ob2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to eat greek food for a reasonable price. You get excellent service, (usually) not too busy if you reserve for early hours (around about 17.30). I paid 75 EUR for two, ranging from appetizers to desserts. Definitely recommend!
(picture includes Gyros, Ribeye, and Chicken fillet.)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhwbXPIRBCKdj6FK4OtyM0iqRexdDAWEZX2DVL&fid=0x0:0xf7ae52f158bc370b"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Caio Souza Cavalcante","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6QSgbKEwnz7-GSpGVlTi518ip2OcpM1HIktCovWp6PAve1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It is a very cozy place with very good staff. The food is ok, but in my opinion it missed salt, but at least they had it on the table so you could take it.

The tomato soup wasn't good, it was too thin and missing taste, but the steak was awesome. I ordered a well done steak and they brought me a very thick one and they surprised me that they managed to make it well done.

The prices are in the average, so it is ok.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPexQ3lxBBCCAan1cswSVlTFtdT_oH7SYB2zsbS&fid=0x0:0xf7ae52f158bc370b"],"When":"2022-2-22"},{"Name":"Victoria Chhim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9el8ACpLWEFpX-qvLMn7xImXd0GE5BdadSJkcKmyrZfYRAKbI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Despite the super loud atmosphere that can be overwhelming when you get in, the food was AMAZING. Aperitif and digestif offered. Nice welcoming! We ordered something to share and, wow. Everything was great! Would recommend that to group of people that are curious about food or just big eaters. It's from two onward. Honestly we had food for two days (being with two persons) üòÖ","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyHcUk9Dh-Uh190JkE8euIryJcfYk31402dBZ6&fid=0x0:0xf7ae52f158bc370b"],"When":"2023-3-23"},{"Name":"chris de ridder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSD51-_7VCxUVWayqZ1ucY8W4-xHuxv26WnSePVPSP1rUSofc_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always good service and food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO10cmucmqLBeq27IUlz0tK1vh4WKB-q2pjNdU5&fid=0x0:0xf7ae52f158bc370b"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"FatsaRock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxo_g36rtO-ULTug1fPMgv1VfKLwAbJXXhlD6XXZr4S4MCeAru=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a cozy and pleasant place with so nice and kind people working there! The food is always great and the service is excellent!! Thank you so much for your hard work and your commitment!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMW6IoA_vt9_yq8HEmxIOqxSokOrn5sI8uyf_E&fid=0x0:0xf7ae52f158bc370b"],"When":"2023-1-29"},{"Name":"Robert ‚ÄúJemimus‚Äù van Jemimus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcEb4qlZl2m_yEGuuSUpxLkA7nxfJG4__STgNDup76sWd68RuK3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Attitude of waiters not great. Almost begrudging level of serive.  Not helpful. No patience. No clear communication. Not attentive in any way.
Food was quite good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ana Basilidze","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQ9rBi-estOOiaaPktj5k7y6Hvxjh714NghobHyxOBekR166Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excelent restaurants and hospitality. We are most thankful to Gian; he is a very kind employee.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Derwort","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlXVQEaA-OTQYtANx3YQG8yqC6Nh2HSKC8YwGAKv9KKO2ME30B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good food, nice vibe and plenty of seats. It is rather big, but it is divided into cosy sections so it doesn't necessarily feel big. It can get quite busy so making a reservation is always recommended. Huge terrace out front at a really quiet location, so perfect for a summer night dinner! üëå","Images":null,"When":""}]

Peco, his wife, and incredible team have the finest selection of wine, food was perfect, and watching how they treat all their customers it‚Äôs clear they enjoy the human touch!
Grazie Mille!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdNulPzH_5Mv6B0dg9nMsiFEzDA2lQPn8YZB2n&fid=0x0:0xbfee43b71be0db2a"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Will ToLive","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSq4QpovIVcmyOKcpgN2OYH4mN_PTf2xfUDjRuWUYDi6vI75Wvcg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great experience... Have to be conservative so not a 5 star review all-around... Some dishes need improvement especially the antipasto. The ice cream could have been of a higher level with homemade Italian ice cream instead of the cheap supermarket stuff. The owner is a great guy! And kids can eat half price!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anika wendorf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIPEeo1h9bKZKO2Myd6l6SA6rmxd7TY3QLDcqXyMfE_YMlVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I visited da peco for the first time. We needed to wait quite long to get the menu cards. I ordered ravioli with sage butter. The plate was cold, the pasta tasted hard and the sage butter was something else - a thick sauce with a strong taste of bouillon cube. I was quite disappointed. Especially for this quite steep price. Not sure I will come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQos2kyKIljOobOkqQnqEdbfgOo4lvBoVYeNk&fid=0x0:0xbfee43b71be0db2a"],"When":"2018-10-14"},{"Name":"Achim Wollenweber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXr_A-AiQufltEkF0UwUo_xeUyGYz3nGjPuF92AdxvTCovcsykp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Place looks nice and luxerious and service is good, that doesn¬¥t mean that the food is amazing. #Ossobuco, with Risotto can¬¥t really recommend it, as the rice was just cooked in water and not like a tasty italian Risotto should be. Meat was not too much for +25EUR and reviews here, mention small portions + my Soft-Drinks, 0.2. The Chef was having such a good time and I guess he saw me salivating over all the delicious food being made, so he started making a little extra of everything and giving it to me to try while I waited. I had trio- fish and it was really good, very tender steamed fish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3hy9UBVBuErcn7JJZUyDtSTLgHSBfbB6d8HsN&fid=0x0:0x35ca7697eb41e248"],"When":"2024-3-3"},{"Name":"Marcel vandenHeuvel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLvEs1D-Kc06-9WHlH5JyoUJe2NKOumZJ8pa8F4V_57zCK7q5E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Gave 1 star because it's not possible to give a worse rating. Breakfast was a mess and this is not a van der valk issue... normally breakfast is great but the crew at this hotel makes it a horrible experience.

Terrible hospitality","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Red Queen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeroVWTTGHj9jrSB0NSZY9B0riSie7J25PCrDPcymInX-nfJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Rooms are clean and bed is comfy, but i really don't like the interior design. [{"Name":"Anna Keszthelyi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNUqly0M-Jaxmx5cOirrRiai_mGgf3nivuldcOvayCnAV0ji4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"very cozy place, it seems that they pay attention to the right design. the service was friendly, the waitress was very nice and attentive, she was in a good mood, we felt pleasant. the food was also excellent, the vegetable side dish was made from very fresh vegetables, which I rarely see in the Netherlands... my food came out a little later, for which the restaurant compensated us all, which was also very nice. we will definitely come back here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8znYEFmoVhF-VnYXtAZ0v3hTyrgpUdAvyhnxG&fid=0x0:0xf426a6e43ea6bc06"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Henry Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEoZn1FYJ3ZQyboPqbhP17Cp1v-Y0ZsOuXvUzWMT56_5gr1Jo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for lunch on a Friday afternoon with my wife and we enjoyed this place! The owners greeted us and were very attentive and welcoming.

For food, we got the Caesar Salad, tuna salad sandwich and smoked salmon sandwich. The Caesar Salad has a hint of anchovies which gives it a more authentic taste. The sandwiches came skillfully presented and tasted delicious.

The atmosphere was cozy, warm, and homey. It had a mountain lodge vibe; they even had a fireplace with real wood burning.

I would recommend this place for lunch and dinner if you have time to enjoy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"HaMID jaan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUs7Rui-eMXqZA2__lSuvNQszbnoPSiaFnNJN8C6GmfNFdUfO4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fresh food, good servings, nice cozy place. [{"Name":"sbn ptrs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ97rPLg9yatoxZ9mVaKUqQpyOKuJOBCK7k41oE-6VUTE1quw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just trust the chef and the owner; take the surprise menu with the wine arrangement, and you will not be disappointed! Had a great evening with a lot of tasty foods and drinks and everything was explained very well. I actually learned something about wines and the taste of pure Italian food! Will definitely come back here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Benjamin L.V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJv7viIMLkYLQThP9DGSfQRbBJaOFcnQc5QAqY0PdqP8IUpfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were looking for a place for dinner at 9 pm on a Thursday. We went to a few places before, and all of them weren't serving food or closed by that time. When we thought we would be having a snackbar (nothing against it, of course), we tried our luck, and they kindly welcomed us for dinner. At that moment, we realised how lucky we were to discover La Passione. Owned by a couple, they make you feel welcome. I remember the host mentioning that to her, every guest becomes part of "La Famiglia." Very friendly, kind, and the patience of a saint, she helped us with the menu. When the food came out, the presentation was spectacular, but the first bite, A-MA-ZING! All the food is homemade and selected meticulously by the chef, and let me tell you, he has a good eye for it! All in all, it was a great experience with great food. If we come back to Heerlen, La Passione will be our very first choice to eat.

Grazie mille famiglia La Passione!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUexYss2BVU-M1ARswP2SZYwBd1P5AbB1CGhHOAc4Pt3DusSppCXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's Italian, a real one. With Italian quality and an Italian chef. I felt home, with the care and the flavours of my country, Italia. Grazie! Loved the Valpolicella Ripasso for their pappardelle al cinghiale (I felt being in Tuscany!) and the Chianti for their outstanding filet with spume of coffee and red wine... We'll be back soon ;)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0p8wIyZ6nOOhVa3oCg4rq9hxEGw38uu8KD4TW&fid=0x0:0xf60f65f7b3a2ebf0"],"When":"2017-11-1"},{"Name":"Kirsteen Easdale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIOGztQdFqNn3ddl4AVHC0z7eDg3iyW5hD1-u-sE81gT6HkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Again, we had a lovely meal here. The atmosphere is cosy, staff are attentive, and most importantly the food is great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andy T.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRrZZk8d58kaQtdSe7MGc-Rgc9UsrFNv6fdeSuc6YHn0X6823D=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If there‚Äôs one restaurant I will never go back to is this one. There is nothing positive to say. From the service to the food to how cold it was. And from the comments we got from the lady that served us we left without having desert or coffee.
And she charged us for more drinks than we had.
If they don‚Äôt change their attitude towards their customers they will be closed in no time.
I haven‚Äôt been so disappointed in a restaurant.
One star is more than they deserve.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bryan de vos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHm3Rc6mAMxfHm5pmu1Wu9u_OdTowYsGND2tsZw7qZEq63piM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was really good and service was nice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO727sIC2CKwyOQ6i6lTs7LEf0WYbhaGAKDwFAk&fid=0x0:0xf60f65f7b3a2ebf0"],"When":"2020-8-23"},{"Name":"Ren√© Kall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDd4gA2bp4y9NJTgRvN6S-9oGG_CBxJ4pLPXvhfbeechCb8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice restaurant with very good Italian food and wine. We went to the restaurant twice for dinner. I personally enjoyed the food a lot, both meet and fish dishes. The service is also remarkable - the waiters were always in a good mood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlnRRoVX7hqYN7RTbbc52cVW70pMoW8gqw8dPO&fid=0x0:0x282e78b4e199f2d7"],"When":"2024-3-4"},{"Name":"Peter J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0A1cZfC0DPvuj8tSExWJOPE_hnemlYDvTzwRSjR2NvmE_S-AK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Customer service employees from hell. We live in Maastricht and wanted to enjoy a nice breakfast on 2nd Pinkster day (National holiday) so we called in advance to make sure they were open. We were told that breakfast would be served until 11:00, so we hopped in the car and drove there (6 people in total)

However, when we arrived we discovered that the restaurant of Auberge de Rousch was closed and only the hotel was open to have breakfast, but OK, then we decided to go there for our breakfast. We arrived at 10:50 and there were people sitting still and the full buffet was still out, BUT we were told that breakfast was no longer served. When we objected and told them we had called in advance, the lady went to her colleague to check and that turned out to be the lady we had spoken to on the phone. Surprisingly we were told that breakfast would be served only until 11:00 LITERALLY and that we could not sit down to eat.

While I understand that there are rules in place there should be room for exceptions within reason and having us (6 people) sit down to have breakfast would hardly have constituted a problem, but instead the employees choose the ridged interpretation and refused to serve us. Disappointing and it speaks volume about how this place sees it guests and the level of service they stand for.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpyWgiI9r05QQtHhsyAWGBUVvRfEwdfsfLofQ5DCu1dpRDKTvf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for a relaxing lunch with great food. Friendly and service minded staff. Can recommend for every season in terms of surroundings and ambiance. Last time visited during winter with a decent amount of snow adding to the location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhxZyYXEBU8r1jfqtuPBcG0Z4m670jH2vAqDlu&fid=0x0:0x282e78b4e199f2d7"],"When":"2024-1-19"},{"Name":"Ricardo Munsel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT1ZSFW4AvEAx_i4Mc5rD2kH75IYQuX6tkjrCNRFZjDbAcyCntLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Maybe because they are not used to the new set-up, but the part we were seated in, there were some things that went wrong or were not properly attended to. It seemed that most guests in our room had the same menu. But they got the order wrong of our table and another table had to wait almost 40 minutes for their main dish. The promised amuse was never presented. We also noticed that the plates of the other guests were richer decorated (cookie on the cream) or got more attention (pepper on the steak) than we did.
The food was nice, but not special. The service did their best to right the wrong but it just didn't do it for us.
We are sure that others will have a better experience than ours. I am not sure if we will return to see if the service has improved.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Enjoying_ MeTime","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJFbFJb9e18AIngoJFEeQTU_bn6XYddJGTJRsUKTN0YcRJ0Ncy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Was here for my coffee break. Terras is surrounded by nature. Love the view ‚ù§
Food quality is ok.
Service needs to be improved. After a long wait...I found out that they actually forgotten my order. Not that crowded tho.

4 star for the view.
3 star for the service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-ppH0x_IRbJviCORN0uOegemPdN2FGJmA7YtK&fid=0x0:0x282e78b4e199f2d7"],"When":"2021-9-10"},{"Name":"Christy M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpT0Fn0zqp3U3GCsoNI90syZ_hdT6D-hto3j1knx0Qvwdvh5q5Tw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff was pleasant, efficient and accommodating. Pumpkin Soup, Entrees with vegetables and potatoes, wine,  bottled water, coffee and cookie tray. Wij komen nog een keer terug.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOvedOY9fdh72nYGJaaA3ygVOHmzyR-fGh4TZy&fid=0x0:0x83e88c1608313710"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Marcel Voncken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhDCr3gk_a9D1l6Nj1_tHt4HDMX7b3WnyzBXhUNWKLQwJduhbp9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Een aangename eetgelegenheid in het centrum van Heerlen. De culinaire ervaring was uitstekend en de porties waren genereus. De prijs-kwaliteitverhouding was zeer gunstig.

Het personeel was uiterst vriendelijk en attent.

De drankprijzen waren enigszins aan de hoge kant, maar dit lijkt een algemene trend te zijn in de horecabranche.

De ambiance was ietwat sober, maar het eten compenseerde dit ruimschoots.

Wij zullen zeker overwegen om in de toekomst opnieuw te dineren bij Pinchos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObhdAyWyHebRKKJVc2hdO-CqNNviJ91870cdET&fid=0x0:0x83e88c1608313710"],"When":"2024-6-19"}]
